data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2-story home featuring 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms with unfinished basement, waiting for your final touch. With a spacious layout, the main floor boasts a modern kitchen, inviting living areas, and a half bath for convenience. Upstairs, you'll find the generously sized bedrooms and well-appointed bathrooms, creating a comfortable and luxurious living space. This home offers the perfect blend of style and functionality for your family's enjoyment. Sold as-is.
